abstract: "Public-safe companion repository for a conservative sports engineering manuscript on deterministic representation packets for sports trajectories under explicit coordinate, threshold, tolerance, score, and staged sensitivity assumptions. The repository includes manuscript drafts, claim-boundary documents, public-safe figure and table views, and staged sensitivity summaries. Trajectory-derived artifacts and private implementation materials are intentionally withheld."
